They expressed the hope that under the leadership of the Guangdong provincial party committee and government, the Guangdong army and people would make concerted efforts in disaster relief; earnestly help flood victims solve their living problems; and go all out to battle floods to ensure the safety of the Bei Jiang dike, Guangzhou city, and the Zhu Jiang Delta. Recently, they repeatedly inquired about the flood situation in the Zhu Jiang valley, particularly that of Bei Jiang and Xi Jiang. Jiang Zemin and Li Peng gave important directives for current flood prevention and disaster relief tasks in Guangdong. 